prodNameC: 免疫特 快速法促甲狀腺素試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Rapid TSH Reagent:
Each barcode-labeled unit contains one bead coated with monoclonal murine anti-TSH antibody. 6.5 mL alkaline phosphatase (bovine calf intestine) conjugated to polyclonal goat anti-TSH in buffer. Two vials (Low and High) of lyophilized human TSH in a serum/buffer matrix.
Repid TSH Sample Diluent:
One vial containing 25 mL of TSH-free serum/buffer matrix.
